Scientific Graphing and Data Analysis, all online.

Plotly lets you analyze data and create scientific graphs, all online and for free. Graphs and datasets can then be shared seamlessly with classmates, teachers, lab mates, or within your organization. Check out our features and see what Plotly can do for your classroom or company.

Easily make graphs with your data in the workspace. Import data from Google Drive or upload Excel or text files. You can apply fits, stats, and functions to your data.
Every element of a Plotly graph is customizable. Change the colors, annotate, write LaTeX, toggle graph ticks, and much more. It's up to you!
